data.description: Welcome home to this 4 yrs new 3-bedroom 2 bath beautiful ranch in a cul-de-sac. This home offers an open floor plan, vaulted ceiling, wood floor though out, ceiling fans, eat in kitchen, custom cabinets, breakfast bar, stainless steel appliances, updated light fixtures, main floor laundry, large master bedroom, walk in closets, luxury master bath with dual vanity, shower/tub combo, full basement with egress window and full rough in. Make your appointment today!!!!
